Cheesecake

Unknown | Makes 1 cheesecake | Takes 30 Minutes

Ingredients

  • 1 graham (or other) crust
  • 2 pkg cream cheese
  • 1/3 c sugar
  • 1 tbls milk
  • 1 tbls vanilla
  • 1 egg

Directions

  1. Mix everything but the crust together. Pour the mix into the crust.
  2. Bake in a preheated oven at 350 for 30 minutes.
  3. Let cool and enjoy.
